query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_components, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT SUBSTRING(code, 1, 1)) as level1_count,
       COUNT(DISTINCT SUBSTRING(code, 1, 3)) as level2_count,
       COUNT(DISTINCT SUBSTRING(code, 1, 5)) as level3_count
FROM building_components;
